			<end-paragraph
				>
			</end-paragraph>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23040024">
			</marker>
			<begin-paragraph class="line-group">
			</begin-paragraph>
			<verse num="24">
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				Scarcely are they planted, scarcely sown,
