				</begin-line>
				Lift up your eyes on high and see:
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				who created these?
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
